title: 30 Z Palette Round Metal Magnetic Metal Stickers for Non-Magnetized Makeup Pans 26 mm For Use With Z Palettes Only
description: Round Metal Stickers are perfect for de-potted shadows, blushes, bronzers, and powders that were not meant for magnetic palettes. Just peel & stick onto the back of the pans for strong adhesion to prevent from products moving. Use a Sharpie and write the color name on the back of the metal sticker for future reference.
